name: Mirror Mirror
description:
This art piece was created as a metaphorical letter to a woman caught in the web of self-doubts and personal complexes... A regular mirror is often used for only one purpose - to seek an honest answer whether one is worthy of someone else's attention, dreams, and desires, when in reality that question can only be answered by the person who is asking that question. 

Always remember, you are the most precious gift a life can give...
